(40, 19, 13, 40, 18, 2, 5, 'little children', 'Children and Humility in Faith', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of little children in relation to faith and humility. In Matthew 19:13, children are brought to Jesus, while Matthew 18:2-5 highlights the necessity of becoming like little children to enter the kingdom of heaven.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
